Package net.jdazher.domain.tasks.response

Interface Response

All Known Implementing Classes:
CreateErrorResponse, CreateTaskResponse
public interface Response
A marker interface representing a generic response in the system.

This interface is intended to be implemented by various response classes to indicate that they represent a response in the application's communication layer.

As a marker interface, it does not define any methods or behavior. Its purpose is to provide a common type for all response classes.
